assment%20Case%20Cost%203%20Lives%20In%20A%20Year%20-%20Including%20Her%20Own%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20stark%20reminder%20that%20tall%20claims%20and%20taller%20promises%20during%20election%20season%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20ground%20realities%2C%20a%20Dalit%20family's%20fight%20for%20justice%20in%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Sagar%20has%20claimed%20three%20lives%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%20--%20the%20latest%20of%20the%20complainant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20now%2020%2C%20filed%20a%20police%20case%20in%202019%20against%20four%20men%2C%20alleging%20that%20they%20had%20harassed%2C%20threatened%20and%20assaulted%20her.%20According%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20complainant%2C%20then%2015%2C%20was%20out%20for%20ablutions%20when%20Azad%20Thakur%2C%20Vishal%20Thakur%2C%20Pushpendra%20Thakur%20and%20Chotu%20Raikwar%20verbally%20abused%20her.%20Vishal%20Thakur%2C%20the%20woman%20alleged%2C%20also%20slapped%20her%20and%20threatened%20her%20against%20going%20to%20the%20cops.%C2%A0Coming%20months%20before%20the%202020%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20case%20became%20a%20subject%20of%20heated%20political%20exchanges%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20Opposition%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20elections%20were%20over%2C%20and%20the%20accused's%20families%20started%20pressuring%20the%20woman%20to%20withdraw%20her%20complaint.%20The%20family%20refused.%20In%20August%20last%20year%2C%20a%20mob%20of%20hundreds%20beat%20the%20woman's%2018-year-old%20brother%20to%20death.%20The%20complainant%20was%20also%20assaulted%20and%20her%20mother%20stripped%20when%20she%20tried%20to%20protect%20her%20son%20during%20the%20attack.%20Amid%20an%20outrage%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20nine%20people%20were%20charged%20with%20murder%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20stringent%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20were%20also%20invoked.%20Two%20people%20were%20arrested%20and%20another%20long%20legal%20fight%20began.%20According%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20accused%20included%20Vikram%20Thakur%2C%20Vijay%20Thakur%2C%20Azad%20Thakur%2C%20Komal%20Thakur%2C%20Lalu%20Khan%2C%20Islam%20Khan%2C%20Golu%20Soni%2C%20Nafis%20Khan%20and%20Waheed%20Khan.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Saturday%2C%20the%20woman's%20uncle%2C%20also%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20mob%20murder%20of%20her%20brother%2C%20received%20a%20call%20from%20one%20Pappu%20Rajak.%20Pappu%20told%20the%20woman's%20uncle%20that%20the%20accused%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bsettle%26quot%3B%20the%20matter.%20The%20woman's%20uncle%20was%20asked%20to%20retract%20his%20testimony.%20When%20he%20refused%2C%20both%20he%20and%20Pappu%20were%20attacked.%20The%20woman's%20uncle%20died%20during%20treatment%2C%20and%20Pappu's%20condition%20is%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20police%20complaint%20by%20the%20family%2C%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20murder%20case%20against%20five%20accused%20---%20Aashiq%20Qureshi%2C%20Bablu%20Bena%2C%20Israel%20Bena%2C%20Faheem%20Khan%20and%20Tantu%20Qureshi.%20One%20of%20them%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20family%2C%20more%20was%20to%20come.%20On%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20the%20woman%20who%20filed%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20back%20in%202019%20fell%20to%20death%20from%20the%20hearse%20van%20carrying%20her%20uncle's%20body.%20She%20was%20bringing%20the%20body%20home%2C%20but%20opened%20the%20van's%20door%20when%20they%20were%20still%2020%20km%20away%20and%20jumped%2C%20according%20to%20some%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELokesh%20Sinha%2C%20Additional%20Superintendent%20Of%20Police%2C%20said%20the%20woman's%20uncle%20had%20died%20of%20injuries%20he%20suffered%20in%20a%20clash%20between%20two%20groups.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20under%20investigation.%20Now%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20in%20the%20hearse%20van%20fell%20and%20die.%20All%20facts%20would%20come%20out%20during%20the%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20death%20has%20sparked%20a%20scathing%20attack%20by%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20Mohan%20Yadav-led%20BJP%20government%20over%20the%20state's%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20While%20top%20Congress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20targeted%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20state%20party%20leader%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20police%20didn't%20act%20even%20after%20the%20woman%20alerted%20them%20about%20pressure%20on%20the%20family.%20State%20Congress%20chief%20Jitu%20Patwari%20has%20demanded%20a%20CBI%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20growing%20outrage%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20set%20to%20visit%20the%20victim's%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716893940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fk6fajct8_mp-dalit-woman-_625x300_28_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-dalit-womans-harassment-case-cost-3-lives-in-a-year-including-her-own-5763812%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20stark%20reminder%20that%20tall%20claims%20and%20taller%20promises%20during%20election%20season%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20ground%20realities%2C%20a%20Dalit%20family's%20fight%20for%20justice%20in%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Sagar%20claimed%20three%20lives%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-dalit-womans-harassment-case-cost-3-lives-in-a-year-including-her-own-5763812%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-dalit-womans-harassment-case-cost-3-lives-in-a-year-including-her-own-5763812%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-dalit-womans-harassment-case-cost-3-lives-in