7.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStarc%20Earns%2024.75%20Crore%2C%20You%2055%20Lakh%26quot%3B%3A%20Rinku's%20Fiery%20Reply%20On%20KKR%20Salary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rinku%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F106742-rinku-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERinku%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20at%20the%20same%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20franchise%20for%207%20years.%20A%20couple%20of%20seasons%20ago%2C%20Rinku%20started%20to%20really%20showcase%20his%20potential%2C%20winning%20matches%20for%20KKR%2C%20and%20his%20consistency%20even%20earned%20India%20call-up.%20Rinku%20remains%20a%20part%20of%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20roster%20too%2C%20though%20as%20reserves.%20Despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Rinku%20is%20among%20the%20finest%20finishers%20in%20India%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20T20%20format%2C%20he%20only%20earns%20a%20salary%20of%2055%20lakh%20at%20KKR.%20His%20IPL%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20earns%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2024.75%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rinku%20decides%20to%20leave%20KKR%20and%20put%20his%20name%20in%20the%20auction%20pool%2C%20even%20a%20Rs%2010%20crore%20bid%20might%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20sign%20him.%20On%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20low%20salary%20he%20gets%20at%20KKR%2C%20Rinku%20gave%20the%20perfect%20example%20of%20his%20mentality%2C%20saying%20even%2050-55%20lakh%20is%20a%20lot%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%2050-55%20lakhs%20is%20a%20lot.%20When%20I%20started%2C%20I%20had%20not%20even%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20earn%20so%20much.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20a%20kid%20and%20if%20I%20got%20even%2010-5%20rupees%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20get%20it%20somehow.%20Now%20I%20am%20getting%2055%20lakh%20rupees%2C%20so%20this%20is%20a%20lot%2C%20I%20should%20be%20happy%20with%20whatever%20God%20gives%20me.%20This%20is%20my%20thinking.%20I%20don't%20think%20at%20all%20that%20I%20should%20have%20got%20this%20much%20money%20or%20that%20much.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20even%20with%2055%20lakh%20rupees.%20When%20I%20didn't%20have%20this%2C%20I%20realized%20the%20value%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jagran.com%2Fcricket%2Finterview-rinku-singh-exclusive-interview-with-jagran-after-win-ipl-2024-final-23726675.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDainik%20Jagaran%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinku%20isn't%20the%20sort%20of%20a%20person%20who%20believes%20in%20running%20after%20money.%20Like%20a%20proverbial%20saint%2C%20he%20highlighted%20that%20people%20come%20and%20leave%20the%20same%20way%2C%20without%20any%20money%20in%20their%20pocket.%20Hence%2C%20staying%20grounded%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20tell%20you%20the%20truth%20today%2C%20then%20all%20this%20is%20an%20illusion.%20You%20did%20not%20bring%20anything%20with%20you%2C%20nor%20will%20you%20take%20anything%20with%20you.%20You%20never%20know%20when%20time%20will%20change.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20you%20have%20to%20go%20back%20the%20same%20way%20you%20came.%20Stay%20grounded%2C%20what%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716892260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnbs8486g_rinku-singh-bcci_625x300_28_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmitchell-starc-earns-24-75-crore-you-55-lakh-rinku-singhs-fiery-reply-on-low-kkr-salary-5763599%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rinku%20Singh%20gets%20an%20IPL%20salary%20of%20INR%2055%20Lakh%2C%20while%20Mitchell%20Starc%20fetches%20Rs%2024.75%20crore%20at%20KKR.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C