Fpakistani-hackers-may-have-hit-3-major-indian-defence-firms-find-out-which-124052801049_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKCR%20Wanted%20To%20Arrest%20BJP's%20BL%20Santosh%26quot%3B%3A%20Big%20Claim%20In%20Phone%20Tapping%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInquiries%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Ftelangana%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelangana%3C%2Fa%3E%20phone-snooping%20row%20have%20thrown%20up%20yet%20another%20explosive%20allegation%20-%20that%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fkcr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EK%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%3C%2Fa%3E%20wanted%20to%20arrest%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbl-santosh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBL%20Santosh%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20force%20a%20%26quot%3Bcompromise%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bget%20rid%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20case%26quot%3B%20against%20his%20daughter%20K%20Kavitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20were%20made%20by%20ex-Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20P%20Radhakrishna%20Rao%20in%20a%20six-page%20confession%20that%20contained%20damning%20claims%2C%20including%20one%20that%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Barm-twisted%20certain%20persons%20creating%20trouble%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%2For%20his%20family%20members%20and%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20-%20arrested%20in%20March%20from%20his%20Banjara%20Hills%20Hyderabad%20home%20-%20also%20claimed%20he%20had%2C%20on%20orders%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20his%20inside%20circle%2C%20been%20active%20in%20%26quot%3Bsuppressing%20dissent%20or%20protest%20or%20agitation%20against%20the%20BRS%20(then%20called%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20or%20TRS)%20and%2For%20its%20government...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Ftelangana-phone-tapping-case-p-radhakrishna-rao-ex-senior-cops-claims-about-telangana-phone-tap-case-kcrs-partys-role-5757938%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Phone%20Tap%20Case%3A%20Ex-Senior%20Cop's%20Claims%20On%20KCR's%20Role%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20senior%20cop%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20City%20Task%20Force%2C%20said%20KCR%2C%20whom%20he%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Epeddayana%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20or%20his%20%26quot%3Belder%26quot%3B%2C%20would%20get%20%26quot%3Birritated%20by%20minor%20dissent%20or%20criticism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BGet%20Rid%20Of%20Case%20Against%20Kavitha%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%20the%20biggest%20flashpoint%20was%20an%20elaborate%20plot-and-counterplot%20drama%20involving%20the%20BRS'%20Tandur%20lawmaker%20Panjugula%20%26quot%3BPilot%26quot%3B%20Rohith%20Reddy%2C%20an%20alleged%20poaching%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20scheming%20to%20entrap%20his%20rivals%20and%20force%20dropping%20of%20charges%20against%20Ms%20Kavitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20sometime%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20October%20(before%20the%202023%20Assembly%20election)%2C%20one%20day%20Prabhakar%20Rao%20told%20me%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20information%20from%20an%20MLA%20that%20some%20persons%20claiming%20to%20be%20influential%20in%20BJP%20(were)%20asking%20him%20to%20leave%20BRS%20and%20join%20(the%20rival%20party)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET%20Prabhakar%20Rao%20was%20then%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Special%20Intelligence%20Branch%20and%20reportedly%20tasked%20by%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20with%20running%20the%20allegedly%20illegal%20phone%20tapping%20operation.%20Prabhakar%20Rao%20-%20expected%20to%20return%20shortly%20from%20the%20United%20States%20-%20has%20been%20named%20as%20'Accused%20No%201'%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp