case%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI%20(which%20reports%20to%20the%20centre)...%20%3Cem%3Epedayanna%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0KCR%20was%20very%20angry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-mla-poaching-case-transferred-to-cbi-by-high-court-3639368%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOn%20Alleged%20Poaching%20Of%20MLAs%20By%20BJP%2C%20KCR%20Faces%20Court%20Setback%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20also%20disbanded%20the%20SIT%2C%20arguing%20it%20could%20not%20ensure%20an%20%26quot%3Bimpartial%26quot%3B%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Reacts%20To%20Claims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Telangana%20leader%20N%20Ramchander%20Rao%20has%20hailed%20Mr%20Rao's%20claims%2C%20declaring%20it%20has%20reinforced%20what%20the%20party%20said%20earlier%20-%20that%20there%20was%20a%20political%20conspiracy%20to%20trap%20leaders%20like%20BL%20Santosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKCR%20tried%20to%20create%20a%20political%20conspiracy...%20we%20maintained%20there%20was%20no%20attempt%20by%20BJP%20to%20poach%20MLAs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%2C%20and%20also%20criticised%20the%20alleged%20phone%20tapping%20as%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%26quot%3B%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Raid'%20On%20Congress%20Poll%20Strategist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20also%20made%20sensational%20claims%20about%20'raids'%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsunil-kanugolu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunil%20Kanugolu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20orchestrated%20the%20Congress'%20thumping%20win%20over%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202023%20Karnataka%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20before%20that%20election%2C%20in%20December%2C%20Mr%20Kanugolu%20reportedly%20made%20posts%20criticising%20KCR%20and%20his%20party.%20These%20posts%20prompted%20illegal%20snooping%20