20within%203%20hours.%20There%20was%20no%20looking%20back%20after%20this.%20Anchal%20went%20on%20to%20take%20all%20her%20exams%20on%20her%20laptop%20without%20the%20assistance%20of%20a%20scribe.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20offered%20half%20an%20hour%20extra%20but%20I%20never%20needed%20it%3B%20I%20was%20always%20one%20of%20the%20first%20students%20to%20finish%20writing%2C%E2%80%9D%20gleams%20Anchal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20I%20work%20in%20Telecom%20Media%20and%20Technology%20Law%2C%20my%20friends%20joke%20that%20my%20entire%20life%20is%20in%20virtual%20space.%20I%20use%20apps%20for%20grocery%2C%20for%20cabs%2C%20for%20everything!%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewer%20technological%20innovations%20and%20services%2C%20especially%20app-based%20deliveries%20and%20services%2C%20have%20made%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311161%2Faneesh-karma-masc-kafo-device-won-infosys-aarohan-social-innovation-award-disabled-people%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindependent%20living%20more%20accessible%20for%20several%20persons%20with%20disability%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-6-1716877825.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-6-1716877825.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-6-1716877825-300x157.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-6-1716877825-500x262.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-6-1716877825-768x402.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-med