ht%20retreats.%20One%20such%20endeavour%20ranges%20from%20%242%2C000%20to%20%244%2C000%20in%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20shorter%20one-day%20version%20too%20that%20costs%20%24222%20per%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKimberly%20Helmus%2C%20one%20of%20the%20participants%2C%20revealed%20what%20she%20feels%20about%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20place%20where%20you%20can%20see%20women%20be%20able%20to%20be%20angry%20like%20that%20and%20it%20not%20be%20condemned%3A%20'She's%20just%20hormonal.%20She's%20just%20unhinged.%20She's%20just%20crazy.%20She's%20just%20on%20her%20period.%20She's%20just%2C%20whatever.'%20This%20was%20a%20place%20where%20you%20were%2C%20probably%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20really%2C%20really%20long%20time%2C%20if%20ever%2C%20able%20to%20scream%20out%20loud%20things%20about%20how%20you%20felt%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Helmus%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20took%20part%20in%20a%20rage%20ritual%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20after%20her%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20ceremonies%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20TikTok%2C%20where%20they%20have%20resonated%20with%20women.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20described%20how%20they%20feel%20to%20see%20other%20women%20vent%20out%20their%20anger%20-%20something%20that%20they%20say%20society%20discourages%20them%20from%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20venting%20out%2C%20some%20unexpected%20emotions%20also%20arise.%20Ms%20Helmus%20said%20instead%20of%20anger%20against%20her%20husband%2C%20she%20felt%20the%20grief%20she'd%20been%20holding%20onto%20since%20witnessing%20the%20death%20of%20a%20friend%20when%20she%20was%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsychotherapists%2C%20however%2C%20say%20there%20is%20one-size-fits-all%20solution%20to%20deal%20with%20anger.%20Psychotherapist%20Stephanie%20Sarkis%20told%20%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20some%20people%20handle%20rage%20with%20activating%20strategies%2C%20like%20hitting%20a%20punching%20bag%20or%20doing%20an%20intense%20workout.%20For%20others%2C%20soothing%20strategies%2C%20like%20deep%20breaths%2C%20slow%20walks%20or%20calm%20music%2C%20work%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716887760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fr4tloig_woman-in-rage-pexels_625x300_28_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Participants%20are%20encouraged%20to%20think%20of%20people%20and%20experiences%20that%20have%20wronged%20them%20and%20to%20scream%20and%20swing%20the%20sticks%20for%20at%20least%2020%20minutes%2C%20or%20until%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20move%20their%20arms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-viral-rage-ritual-trend-has-women-screaming-smashing-sticks-5763242%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zee%20Sets%20%E2%80%98Dhadak%202%E2%80%99%20for%20November%20Theatrical%20Release%20%E2%80%93%20Global%20Bulletin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716887166000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FDhadak-2-Artisti-impression-2x3cr.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236017295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ROMANTIC%20REUNION%20India%E2%80%99s%20Zee%20Studios%20has%20set%20a%20late%20November%20theatrical%20release%20for%20%E2%80%9CDhadak%202%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20romance%20film%20challenging%20societal%20norms.%20The%20film%20is%20a%20sequel%20to%202016%20hit%20%E2%80%9CDhadak%2C%E2%80%9D