a%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sponge%20gourd)%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20%3Cem%3Evalor%20papdi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(field%20beans)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekakdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Armenian%20cucumber)%2C%20etc%20in%20this%20season%20(May-end).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBoth%20watermelon%20and%20muskmelon%20are%20fruit%20plants%20and%20can%20easily%20be%20grown%20on%20terraces.%20After%20cleaning%20the%20seeds%2C%20let%20them%20dry%20on%20tissue%20paper.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet%20the%20vegetables%20like%20cucumber%2C%20ridge%20gourd%2C%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20okra%2C%20and%20different%20types%20of%20beans%20dry%20on%20the%20plant%20instead%20of%20plucking%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20scooping%20out%20seeds%2C%20keep%20them%20in%20a%20clean%20and%20airtight%20plastic%20or%20glass%20container.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnupama-Desai-1-1716297393-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350675%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20scooping%20out%20seeds%2C%20keep%20them%20in%20a%20clean%20and%20airtight%20plastic%20or%20glass%20container.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWait%20until%20vegeta