2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20days%20were%20not%20as%20grand%20as%20I%20had%20hoped%20for%20them%20to%20be.%20But%20what%20I%20focussed%20on%20was%20providing%20quality%20service%20to%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20eatery%20has%20distributed%20over%2010%2C000%20free%20dosas%20since%202018.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdosas-for-free-1716358203-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350696%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20eatery%20has%20distributed%20over%2010%2C000%20free%20%3Cem%3Edosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Esince%202018.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20he%20started%20chatting%20with%20a%20young%20guest.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20back%20in%202018%20and%20the%20elections%20were%20going%20on.%20I%20started%20to%20chat%20with%20the%20young%20man%20and%20noticed%20that%20he%20had%20not%20voted.%20I%20inquired%20why%20and%20he%20simply%20said%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20vote%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20questioning%2C%20Krishnaraj%20realised%20t