0diagnosis%20was%20shock%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20helplessness%20and%20a%20desire%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20for%20her%20child.%20Sushma%20would%20take%20him%20for%20therapy%20daily%20and%20wait%20outside%20for%20three%20hours%20of%20the%20appointment.%20A%20few%20months%20of%20this%20gruelling%20schedule%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20resident%20drained%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20felt%20depressed%2C%20lost%20interest%20in%20her%20daily%20activities%2C%20stopped%20eating%20well%2C%20which%20all%20led%20to%20weight%20loss%20as%20well.%20A%20gynaecologist%20told%20her%20that%20she%20must%20pick%20up%20a%20hobby%20and%20do%20something%20that%20interests%20her.%20This%20advice%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20life-changing%20one%2C%20which%20ignited%20a%20deep-rooted%20passion%20in%20her.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20gardening%20as%20it%20would%20come%20with%20an%20added%20advantage%20of%20giving%20her%20son%20fresh%2C%20organic%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20to%20eat.%20Starting%20with%20a%20money%20plant%20in%202018%2C%20the%20engineer%20slowly%20grew%20to%20realise%20that%20she%20had%20a%20green%20thumb.%20From%20indoor%20plants%2C%20she%20branched%20to%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20on%20the%201%2C000%20square%20feet%20terrace%20of%20her%20rented%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20green%20haven%20with%20over%20300%20plants%2C%2070%20of%20which%20are%20fruit%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20Sushma%20with%20a%20much-needed%20outlet%20for%20her%20worries%2C%20she%20spends%20three%20hours%20a%20day%20tending%20to%20her%20darling%20plants%2C%20all%20on%20her%20own.%20Her%20passion%20also%20led%20to%20an%20Instagram%20account%20%40glitters.of.nature%20which%20has%20over%204%20lakh%20followers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20to%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F3039